  "title": "Velvety Umami Adventurous Fish Stir-fry",
  "description": "This Tunisian-inspired dish features a garlic-rich sauce that marries perfectly with pescatarian-friendly fish for an adventurous and umami-packed meal.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
